and the forehead drops down towards the earth.  The gaze is to the back.</p></li></ul><ul><li><h5>Benefits:</h5><p class='text'>Tones and strengthens the standing leg.  Improves flexibility.  Opens the hips.</p></li></ul></section>        </section>

